<!-- INDICATORS -->
<section id="indicators" class="alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="sec-head fi">
      <span class="sec-tag">// 03 / technical tools</span>
      <h2 class="sec-title">KEY <span class="c">INDICATORS</span></h2>
      <p class="sec-desc">Master these before adding more. Signal stacking without understanding is noise, not edge.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ind-grid">

      <div class="ind fi">
        <div class="ind-top"><div class="ind-name">EMA</div><div class="ind-type">Trend</div></div>
        <p class="ind-desc">Exponential Moving Average weights recent price heavier. Reacts faster than SMA. The backbone of most trend-following systems globally.</p>
        <div class="ind-set-row"><div class="ind-set">Settings: 9 / 20 / 50 / 200 | Use: Trend direction, dynamic S&amp;R, crossovers</div><button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyIndSetting(this,'9 / 20 / 50 / 200')">📋 Copy</button></div>
      </div>

      <div class="ind fi">
        <div class="ind-top"><div class="ind-name">RSI</div><div class="ind-type">Oscillator</div></div>
        <p class="ind-desc">Relative Strength Index oscillates 0–100. Measures momentum speed. Best used for divergence signals — not just overbought/oversold readings.</p>
        <div class="ind-set-row"><div class="ind-set">Period: 14 | OB: &gt;70 | OS: &lt;30 | Divergence is the real signal</div><button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyIndSetting(this,'RSI Period: 14, OB: 70, OS: 30')">📋 Copy</button></div>
      </div>

      <div class="ind fi">
        <div class="ind-top"><div class="ind-name">VWAP</div><div class="ind-type">Intraday</div></div>
        <p class="ind-desc">Volume Weighted Average Price — the institutional benchmark. Institutions judge their fills against it. Above = bullish bias. Resets daily.</p>
        <div class="ind-set-row"><div class="ind-set">Resets daily | Use: Intraday bias, institutional entries, mean reversion</div><button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyIndSetting(this,'VWAP: Daily reset, intraday bias')">📋 Copy</button></div>
      </div>

      <div class="ind fi">
        <div class="ind-top"><div class="ind-name">ATR</div><div class="ind-type">Volatility</div></div>
        <p class="ind-desc">Average True Range measures volatility — not direction. Sets stops that adapt to current conditions, not arbitrary fixed amounts.</p>
        <div class="ind-set-row"><div class="ind-set">Period: 14 | Stop: 1.5–2.5× ATR | Adapts to volatility regime</div><button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyIndSetting(this,'ATR Period: 14, Stop: 1.5-2.5x ATR')">📋 Copy</button></div>
      </div>

      <div class="ind fi">
        <div class="ind-top"><div class="ind-name">MACD</div><div class="ind-type">Momentum</div></div>
        <p class="ind-desc">Measures momentum via EMA relationships. Histogram shows acceleration — the leading signal within MACD that most traders ignore.</p>
        <div class="ind-set-row"><div class="ind-set">12/26/9 default | Histogram flip + crossover | Look for divergence</div><button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyIndSetting(this,'MACD: 12/26/9')">📋 Copy</button></div>
      </div>

      <div class="ind fi">
        <div class="ind-top"><div class="ind-name">BB</div><div class="ind-type">Volatility</div></div>
        <p class="ind-desc">Bollinger Bands: 20-period SMA ± 2 standard deviations. Price visits outer bands 5% of the time. Squeeze = breakout incoming.</p>
        <div class="ind-set-row"><div class="ind-set">20 SMA ± 2 StdDev | Squeeze = bands converging | Walk bands in trends</div><button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyIndSetting(this,'BB: 20 SMA, 2 StdDev')">📋 Copy</button></div>
      </div>

      <div class="ind fi">
        <div class="ind-top"><div class="ind-name">FIBO</div><div class="ind-type">Price Tool</div></div>
        <p class="ind-desc">Fibonacci retracement levels mark potential S/R within pullbacks. The 0.618 (golden ratio) is the most respected level among professional traders.</p>
        <div class="ind-set-row"><div class="ind-set">Key: 0.236 / 0.382 / 0.5 / 0.618 / 0.786 | Draw swing high to low</div><button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyIndSetting(this,'Fib: 0.236 / 0.382 / 0.5 / 0.618 / 0.786')">📋 Copy</button></div>
      </div>

      <div class="ind fi">
        <div class="ind-top"><div class="ind-name">STOCH</div><div class="ind-type">Oscillator</div></div>
        <p class="ind-desc">Stochastic oscillator compares closing price to range over a period. Works best in ranging markets. Avoid using in strong trends.</p>
        <div class="ind-set-row"><div class="ind-set">14,3,3 default | OB: &gt;80 | OS: &lt;20 | Crossovers near extremes</div><button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyIndSetting(this,'Stoch: 14,3,3 | OB:80 OS:20')">📋 Copy</button></div>
      </div>

      <div class="ind fi">
        <div class="ind-top"><div class="ind-name">ICHIMOKU</div><div class="ind-type">Multi-Signal</div></div>
        <p class="ind-desc">All-in-one Japanese system: trend, momentum, S/R in one view. The cloud (Kumo) projects future levels. Complex but extremely powerful once mastered.</p>
        <div class="ind-set-row"><div class="ind-set">5 components: Tenkan, Kijun, Senkou A&amp;B, Chikou | Cloud = trend bias</div><button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyIndSetting(this,'Ichimoku: 9,26,52,26')">📋 Copy</button></div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

